headline: Maggie Anderson Joins JLL Partners as an Operating Partner
summary: NEW YORK, August 11, 2025--JLL Partners, LLC ("JLL" or the "Firm"), a New York-based middle market private equity firm focused on investing in businesses in the healthcare, aerospace and defense, and business services sectors, today announced that Maggie Anderson has joined the Firm as an Operating Partner.
